-- Deutsche Boerse CFO says will not force NYSE deal
-- 
-- Wed Dec 7, 2011 11:17am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/12/07/us-deutscheboerse-nyse-idUSTRE7B61GG20111207

 

 FRANKFURT  (Reuters) - Deutsche Boerse Chief Financial Officer Gregor Pottmeyer said the industrial logic of a takeover of NYSE Euronext should not be undermined by heavy handed antitrust concessions. 
 "We want this transaction, but not at all costs," Pottmeyer said in a statement on Wednesday. (Reporting By Marilyn Gerlach)